{"nodes": [{"id": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_document", "label": "Design", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_context", "label": "Context", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": "line 1", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "`src/buffer.ts` already contains most pure text-editing primitives and Vim operation helpers. `src/vim-editor.ts` and `src/render.ts` still import low-level helpers, which keeps behavior split across adapter, rendering, and buffer layers. This change deepens `buffer.ts` into a prompt buffer operation module so text behavior lives where it can be unit-tested without Pi runtime concerns. Current constraints:"}, {"id": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_goals_non_goals", "label": "Goals / Non-Goals", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": "line 12", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "**Goals:** - Define cohesive buffer operation APIs for navigation, visual selection/editing, linewise operations, operator-motion operations, and paste."}, {"id": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_decisions", "label": "Decisions", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": "line 28", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "### Operation API replaces helper composition at call sites Expose prompt-buffer operations that return existing domain shapes (`Position`, `EditResult`, `VimRegister`, summaries/ranges) instead of forcing callers to compose low-level helpers. Navigation operations should cover buffer start/end, first non-blank, matching pair, and motion resolution. Editing operations should cover visual ranges, line ranges, operator-motion delete/yank/change, and paste before/after."}, {"id": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_operation_api_replaces_helper_composition_at_call_sites", "label": "Operation API replaces helper composition at call sites", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": "line 30", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Expose prompt-buffer operations that return existing domain shapes (`Position`, `EditResult`, `VimRegister`, summaries/ranges) instead of forcing callers to compose low-level helpers. Navigation operations should cover buffer start/end, first non-blank, matching pair, and motion resolution. Editing operations should cover visual ranges, line ranges, operator-motion delete/yank/change, and paste before/after. Rationale: call sites describe user intent, while buffer module owns text mechanics and "}, {"id": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_keep_low_level_helpers_private_unless_cross_module_need_is_proven", "label": "Keep low-level helpers private unless cross-module need is proven", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": "line 38", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "`splitText`, `joinLines`, `clampPosition`, `comparePositions`, range normalization, and offset conversion are implementation details unless another module has a stable reason to depend on them. Rendering may keep a small selection/range surface if needed, but should not duplicate buffer semantics. Rationale: smaller public surface makes future changes easier and clarifies module boundaries."}, {"id": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_tests_target_operation_contracts", "label": "Tests target operation contracts", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": "line 46", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Update `test/buffer.test.ts` to cover operation-level contracts for navigation, visual operations, linewise operations, operator-motion operations, and paste. Keep adapter tests focused on Pi integration, mode dispatch, and delegated shortcuts. Rationale: pure text behavior should be fast, deterministic, and independent of Pi runtime."}, {"id": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_risks_trade_offs", "label": "Risks / Trade-offs", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": "line 54", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "- Public helper removal may break tests or call sites unexpectedly \u2192 migrate call sites in small groups and run typecheck/tests after each group. - Operation API could become too broad \u2192 group by prompt editing intent and avoid exposing generic helpers unless needed. - Visual rendering still needs range data \u2192 keep rendering-facing API narrow and explicit."}, {"id": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_migration_plan", "label": "Migration Plan", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": "line 61", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "1. Inventory external imports from `src/buffer.ts`. 2. Add operation-level APIs around existing behavior without changing semantics. 3. Move `src/vim-editor.ts` and `src/render.ts` to operation-level calls."}, {"id": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_open_questions", "label": "Open Questions", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": "line 70", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "- Should rendering consume explicit visual highlight segments from `buffer.ts`, or only normalized ranges/summaries? Decide during implementation based on lowest coupling. - Should operation grouping use one object namespace or named functions? Prefer named functions unless call sites show object grouping improves clarity."}, {"id": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_ref_src_buffer_ts", "label": "buffer.ts", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": "line 3", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_ref_src_vim_editor_ts", "label": "vim-editor.ts", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": "line 3", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_ref_src_render_ts", "label": "render.ts", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": "line 3", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}], "edges": [{"source": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_document", "target": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_context", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": "line 1", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_document", "target": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_goals_non_goals", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": "line 12", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_document", "target": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_decisions", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": "line 28", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_document", "target": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_operation_api_replaces_helper_composition_at_call_sites", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": "line 30", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_document", "target": "2026_05_27_deepen_buffer_ts_prompt_buffer_module_design_keep_low_level_helpers_private_unless_cross_module_need_is_proven", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-27-deepen-buffer-ts-prompt-buffer-module/design.md", "source_location": 